https://blog.csdn.net/qq_36840228/article/details/121038844
https://blog.csdn.net/qq1010830256/article/details/127212671

sudo yum update
sudo apt install certbot

创建通配符证书
sudo certbot certonly -w /etc/letsencrypt/live/yuelili.com -d "*.yuelili.com" --manual --preferred-challenges dns-01  --server https://acme-v02.api.letsencrypt.org/directory

certbot certonly -w /etc/letsencrypt/live/www.yuelili.com -d www.yuelili.com -d yuelili.com --manual --preferred-challenges dns-01  --server https://acme-v02.api.letsencrypt.org/directory

然后添加DNS记录

位置: /etc/letsencrypt/live/yuelili.com

配置nginx
ssl_certificate /etc/letsencrypt/live/yuelili.com/fullchain.pem;
ssl_certificate_key /etc/letsencrypt/live/yuelili.com/privkey.pem;

检测
certbot renew

定时检测
sudo crontab -e
0 0 * * * certbot renew --quiet

证书管理
查看 sudo certbot certificates
删除 sudo certbot delete --cert-name yuelili.com
